snippet.textDisplay: You guys should really pay attention to the instruments tones. Could have lifted this song if used a more raw bass tone with some slap-pop riffs. Rest of the bass line could have been better too. Also, recording acoustic is always best using a mic rather than the output from pickup. Gives you more of an organic sound. The vocals and lead are very good and I like how verses blend into bridge and provide proper lift for the chorus. Great job! Expecting more great music from Coke Studio.
